  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 425°F (220°C).",
    "Toss the carrots, bell peppers, and broccoli with 1 tablespoon of vegetable oil, salt, and black pepper on a baking sheet and roast for 20 minutes.",
    "In a large pan, heat 1 tablespoon of vegetable oil over medium heat and sauté the onion, garlic, and ginger until softened.",
    "Add the coconut milk, fish sauce, brown sugar, soy sauce, curry powder, and chili flakes to the pan and stir to combine.",
    "Add the roasted vegetables to the pan and stir to coat with the sauce.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a stone bowl dolsot and top with fresh cilantro and a squeeze of lime juice.",
    "Serve with steaming hot rice and enjoy!"
  ],
